{
  "doc_id": "59528",
  "text": "Heterozygous SNPs were phased using the mapped Nanopore reads with HapCut2 commit: c2e6608 [CITATION_1] and converted to VCF format with WhatsHap v0.16 [CITATION_2] . New consensus sequences were called for each haplotype from the phased SNPs and the nanopore reads were binned according to which haplotype they mapped best. The two B. anomalus haplotypes were then independently reassembled from the haplotype-binned nanopore reads using the method described for the other species.",
